hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: I was made redundant two months ago skelaxin liver disease Kenichi Nagahiro, chief engineer on this company's first-ever diesel, admitted he hated diesels and designed the new 1.6-litre engine to be as close as possible in performance, noise and emissions to a petrol engine. So it has proved with this twin-cam unit, which has been carefully designed with reduced internal friction and optimised spray injection to be more fuel efficient. The result gives 118bhp/221lb ft, with a Combined fuel consumption of 62.8mpg, a top speed of 113mph and 0-62mph in 11.2sec.
